Description:

This program is a message management and viewer system. The system is comprised
of (1) Post program, (2) add author, and (3) python viewer with the addition of the
Web interface.


Compilation:

This program can be compiled without error from the A3 folder:

 by typing "make".



Usage:

The program can be run by executing the following (from the
A3 folder):

    1. Post Program

        ./post <username>

    2. Add Author

        ./addauthor <-r to remove> <username>

    3. Python Viewer

        ./view <username>

    4. Web Interface

        Access at index.php
